column5: Clean queen bed, walk-in closet, dresser, and private full bath which is located down the stairs from room. Austin live oak tree view from every window. Hiking trails, community swimming pool, tennis, basketball court, all within walking distance of the house. Oasis Restaurant and Lake Travis Lake within 5 minutes. We are a friendly mature couple w/ friendly dogs.
column8: Cozy Clean Queen Room with view of Texas Live Oaks
